research_municipality_step.notes: Middletown Township, NJ operates under the Township Committee form of government, which consists of five members elected at-large. The Mayor and Deputy Mayor are selected annually by the Township Committee from among its members. The listed officials reflect the leadership for 2026, as established at the annual reorganization meeting on January 4, 2026.
